# Pas 2

## Comprovar contenidors

```bash
docker container ps
```

El contenidor MySQL ha d’estar en execució.


 ⬇️

----

#### Sortida

<pre>
profe@docker-sxm:~/dam/projecte-botiga-jpardo20/sql$ docker container ps
CONTAINER ID   IMAGE                          COMMAND                  CREATED      STATUS      PORTS                                                  NAMES
2cb1e663215b   projecte-botiga-jpardo20-web   "docker-php-entrypoi…"   7 days ago   Up 7 days   0.0.0.0:8080->80/tcp, :::8080->80/tcp                  projecte-botiga-jpardo20-web-1
461b870afa1c   mysql:8                        "docker-entrypoint.s…"   7 days ago   Up 7 days   0.0.0.0:3306->3306/tcp, :::3306->3306/tcp, 33060/tcp   projecte-botiga-jpardo20-db-1
profe@docker-sxm:~/dam/projecte-botiga-jpardo20/sql$
</pre>

---

# Pas 3

## Importar fitxer

```bash
docker compose exec -T db mysql -u root -pprofe < sql/hotel_reserves.sql
```

 ⬇️

----

#### Sortida

<pre>
profe@docker-sxm:~/dam/projecte-botiga-jpardo20$ docker compose exec -T db mysql -u root -pprofe < sql/hotel_reserves.sql
mysql: [Warning] Using a password on the command line interface can be insecure.
profe@docker-sxm:~/dam/projecte-botiga-jpardo20
</pre>

---

# Pas 4

## Verificació

Entrar de nou a MySQL:

```bash
docker compose exec db mysql -u root -p
```

